{"tid":1710207,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"官方宣佈摩迪擊敗C朗同美斯，奪得今年金足獎","createTime":"2019-11-12T06:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T07:44:21.000Z","uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f1b83d69a001bfa4cd033e7fa8561bc738f28220","tid":1710207,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"據《馬卡報》消息，皇馬球星摩迪迪（Luka Modric）將在當地時間本週二，前往摩納哥領取金足獎。<br />\n<br />\n  金足獎是用來表彰那些表現最好的29歲以上的球員，今年已經是該獎項的第17個年頭。<br />\n<br />\n  今年的金足獎頒獎嘉賓包括艾達菲尼、莫拉塞和韋拉等名人，他們將把獎盃頒發給摩迪。<br />\n<br />\n  卡雲尼（Edinson Cavani）、卡斯拿斯（Iker Casillas）、保方（Gianluigi Buffon）、伊度奧（Samuel Eto'o）、恩尼斯達（Andres Iniesta）、杜奧巴（Drogba）、伊巴謙莫域（Zlatan Ibrahimovic）、傑斯（Ryan Giggs）和朗拿甸奴（Ronaldinho）等名宿都曾獲得過金足獎。"},{"pid":"63bdedcd47c2666668008532429497dbf2640bc0","tid":1710207,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:21:09.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"2889a5eef92189fa094ed4a6bbd993368b44de62","tid":1710207,"uid":204856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"邊撚個摩迪迪"},{"pid":"5b18b00123955d0f78fa87c1c6d6faa933cc7e4d","tid":1710207,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2889a5eef92189fa094ed4a6bbd993368b44de62","tid":1710207,"uid":204856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"邊撚個摩迪迪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:29:16.000Z","msg":"烏迪迪親戚"},{"pid":"21a04350f8c7b7f59e8d5ea314c949b055a6a97a","tid":1710207,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b18b00123955d0f78fa87c1c6d6faa933cc7e4d","tid":1710207,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2889a5eef92189fa094ed4a6bbd993368b44de62","tid":1710207,"uid":204856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"邊撚個摩迪迪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:29:16.000Z","msg":"烏迪迪親戚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:29:52.000Z","msg":"斷腳狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/no